  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if closure of deep neck infection incisions at the
      time of extraoral drain removal has any impact on rates of reinfection and to determine if
      this treatment will have any impact on scar formation and qualitative measures of pain or
      impact on quality of life during the post-operative healing period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
