  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  deep neck space infection

          -  who require a conservative unilateral submandibular neck incision to access affected
             deep fascial neck spaces

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant females

          -  cognitively impaired individuals

          -  deep neck space infections which require bilateral neck incisions, large neck apron
             incisions, or placement of negative pressure therapy.
